# Currency Converter Plan

Android-only React Native + Expo + TypeScript currency viewer. **Base currency: KRW.** Shows rate cards for **USD** and **JPY** (EUR / GBP hidden for now).

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Choice |
|-------|--------|
| Framework | React Native 0.86 (Expo SDK 57) |
| Language | TypeScript (strict) |
| Platform | **Android only** (`platforms: ["android"]`) |
| Build / OTA | EAS Build (`eas.json`) |
| Rates API | [Frankfurter](https://www.frankfurter.app/) — no API key |
| Calendar | `react-native-calendars` |
| Safe area | `react-native-safe-area-context` |
| Haptics | `expo-haptics` |
| Theming | `useColorScheme` + `src/theme/colors.ts` |

Bundle ID: `com.mike008.currencyconverter`

## Display Rules

| Currency | Card label | KRW calculation |
|----------|------------|-----------------|
| USD | `$1` | `krwPerUnit.USD × 1` |
| JPY | `¥100` | `krwPerUnit.JPY × 100` |

- EUR / GBP — add later in `currencies.ts`; not shown in UI
- API: `KRW→foreign`; invert to `krwPerUnit` (`1 / rate`)
- **2 cards** (USD, JPY), `CARD_HEIGHT = 200`, `CARD_GAP = 16`
- Pull-to-refresh reloads current view (today or selected date)

### 기준일 & Calendar

- **기준일** badge — prominent blue style; tap opens calendar modal
- Calendar opens to **selected/displayed date month** (`selectedDate ?? rates.date`)
- Selectable: weekdays only, `MIN_RATE_DATE` (1999-01-04) through today
- Disabled: weekends, TARGET/ECB holidays, future dates (`rateCalendar.ts`)
- API: `/latest` (today) or `/{YYYY-MM-DD}` (historical)
- **오늘 환율** button — visible when viewing a past date; calls `resetToLatest()`
- **새로고침** banner — when app stays open past midnight (`needsTodayRefresh`); fetches `/latest`

### Safe Area (Android edge-to-edge)

- `edgeToEdgeEnabled=true` in `android/gradle.properties`
- `App.tsx`: `SafeAreaProvider` + `initialWindowMetrics`
- `HomeScreen`: `SafeAreaView` edges `top`, `left`, `right`, `bottom`
- `RateDateCalendarModal`: bottom `SafeAreaView` on sheet (Modal is outside parent safe area)

## Architecture

| Path | Role |
|------|------|
| `App.tsx` | SafeAreaProvider, StatusBar, HomeScreen entry |
| `src/types/index.ts` | `CurrencyCode` (`USD` \| `JPY`), `CurrencyConfig`, `ExchangeRates` |
| `src/constants/currencies.ts` | Card metadata (symbols, colors, display amounts) |
| `src/services/exchangeRateApi.ts` | Frankfurter fetch (`latest` or `/{date}`) + invert |
| `src/hooks/useExchangeRates.ts` | Load / refresh / selectDate / resetToLatest / needsTodayRefresh |
| `src/hooks/useLocalToday.ts` | Local date tracking (60s interval + AppState active) |
| `src/utils/formatCurrency.ts` | `₩` formatting (`ko-KR`), date label |
| `src/utils/rateCalendar.ts` | Selectable dates, TARGET holidays, month marked dates |
| `src/components/CurrencyCard.tsx` | Single currency card UI |
| `src/theme/colors.ts` | Light / dark color tokens |
| `src/hooks/useAppTheme.ts` | `useColorScheme` wrapper |
| `src/components/CurrencyCardSkeleton.tsx` | Pulsing skeleton card |
| `src/components/SkeletonBone.tsx` | Animated skeleton block |
| `src/utils/haptics.ts` | Success haptic on refresh |
| `src/components/RateDateCalendarModal.tsx` | Calendar bottom sheet (Korean locale, themed) |
| `src/screens/HomeScreen.tsx` | Header, date badge, refresh banner, card stack, last-fetched time |

Keep **rate math in service/utils**, not in components.

