## Commands

```bash
npm install
npm start                    # Expo dev server
npm run android              # expo start --android
npm run typecheck            # tsc --noEmit

npx expo prebuild --platform android   # generate android/ folder
npx expo run:android                   # local native build + run

eas build -p android --profile preview
eas build -p android --profile production
```

## Conventions

- Portrait only
- Minimize scope per change; match existing file layout
- Run `npm run typecheck` after TS changes
- Native module / `android/` changes → new EAS build; JS-only → EAS Update eligible
- No `CLAUDE.md` / `.claude/` — Cursor rules only (this file)
